OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHorizon was not robust,    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsays ex-Post Office boss   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The person in charge of getting the    
OL,6, Horizon system up and running has said 
OL,7, he should not have told the Post Office
OL,8, board the system was "robust" in 1999. 
OL,10,FDavid Miller was recorded as saying the
OL,11,Fsystem was "fit for purpose" at a board
OL,12,Fmeeting in July 1999 after testing.    
OL,14,FHowever, Mr Miller admitted he was     
OL,15,Faware that sub-postmasters were having 
OL,16,Fproblems with it a month before.       
OL,18,FFor more than 15 years from 1999, the  
OL,19,FPost Office insisted Horizon was robust
OL,20,Fwhen prosecuting sub-postmasters.      
